{
  "text": "It is difficult to determine a rule for measuring the two pairs of stress and strain values. In the paper [CITATION_1] , the authors have measured the values of stress at 3% and 10% strain. However, when the tests are made in a number of different modes, this rule can not be applied.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "137333940"
